  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Made from a soft, grey fabric, this cloak has an almost imperceptible glimmer, like frost on a winter morning.</p><p><strong>Powers:</strong></p><ul><li><strong>Winter's Veil:</strong> Grants a +2 competence bonus to Survival checks.</li><li><strong>Cold Comfort:</strong> Provides resistance 15 to cold damage.</li></ul><p><strong>History:</strong> Misty Snowfoot, the group's ranger, donned this cloak, allowing her to thrive in the harshest winter conditions and protect her friends from the cold.</p><img src=\"Art%20-%20Items/cloaks/cloak_childs_charcoal_gray_fleece_traveling_.webp\" />",
